From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: tim2tox-bootstrap <bootstrap@local>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 09:00:00 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 10/10] Fix onGroupCreated on JOIN tip and tolerate missing
 opUser in V2TimMemberInvited.fromJson

Two singleton-path regressions surfaced once 0008 let GroupTipsEvent
fall through to the SDK's `NativeLibraryManager._notifyGroupTips`
dispatcher (binary-replacement path).

Symptoms in tim2tox auto_tests Phase 5/9 conference scenarios
(`scenario_toxav_conference_virtual_test`,
`scenario_conference_virtual_test`,
`scenario_conference_simple_virtual_test`):

  1. The local creator never received `onGroupCreated`. C++
     `OnGroupCreated` (`ffi/dart_compat_listeners.cpp`) emits a JOIN
     tip with an empty `memberList` and an empty `opMember.userID`
     to signal "group was just created by me". The Platform-path
     `Tim2ToxSdkPlatform` already translates that shape to
     `onGroupCreated`, but `_notifyGroupTips`'s JOIN case only fires
     `onMemberEnter` when `groupMemberList.isNotEmpty`, so this
     event was silently dropped on the singleton path.

  2. `type 'Null' is not a subtype of type 'Map<dynamic, dynamic>'`
     in `V2TimMemberInvited.fromJson` when an invite-result callback
     arrived without an `opUser` field. The crash aborted the entire
     callback dispatch via the outer try/catch in
     `_handleNativeMessage`.

Fix (mirrors prior null-tolerance patches 0007 and 0009):

  - `_notifyGroupTips` JOIN case: when both `groupMemberList` is
    empty and `opUser.userID` is empty, fire `_groupListener?.onGroupCreated(groupID)`.
    Otherwise keep existing `onMemberEnter` behavior.
  - `V2TimMemberInvited.fromJson`: default `json['opUser']` to `{}`
    before passing into `V2TimGroupMemberInfo.fromJson`. The inner
    constructor already tolerates an empty map.

After this fix, Phase 5 `scenario_toxav_conference_virtual_test`
and Phase 9 conference scenarios pass on both Platform and
binary-replacement paths.
---
 lib/models/v2_tim_member_invited.dart                  | 2 +-
 lib/native_im/bindings/native_library_manager.dart     | 5 ++++-
 2 files changed, 5 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/lib/models/v2_tim_member_invited.dart b/lib/models/v2_tim_member_invited.dart
--- a/lib/models/v2_tim_member_invited.dart
+++ b/lib/models/v2_tim_member_invited.dart
@@ -21,7 +21,7 @@
   V2TimMemberInvited.fromJson(Map json) {
     json = Utils.formatJson(json);
     groupID = json['groupID'] ?? '';
-    opUser = V2TimGroupMemberInfo.fromJson(json['opUser']);
+    opUser = V2TimGroupMemberInfo.fromJson(json['opUser'] ?? {});
     if (json['memberList'] != null) {
       memberList = List.empty(growable: true);
       json['memberList'].forEach((v) {
diff --git a/lib/native_im/bindings/native_library_manager.dart b/lib/native_im/bindings/native_library_manager.dart
--- a/lib/native_im/bindings/native_library_manager.dart
+++ b/lib/native_im/bindings/native_library_manager.dart
@@ -1212,7 +1212,10 @@
       case GroupTipsElemType.V2TIM_GROUP_TIPS_TYPE_JOIN:
         // 剔除自己
         groupMemberList.removeWhere((member) => member.userID == loginUser);
-        if (groupMemberList.isNotEmpty) {
+        final opUserID = opUser.userID ?? '';
+        if (groupMemberList.isEmpty && opUserID.isEmpty) {
+          _groupListener?.onGroupCreated(groupID);
+        } else if (groupMemberList.isNotEmpty) {
           _groupListener?.onMemberEnter(groupID, groupMemberList);
         }

